    Connections
    This interface models a situation where a set of objects ("sites") maintains a set of connections between the objects.
    TypedUF<T>
    TypedUF is an extension of the UF interface where elements are not limited to integers, but can be represented by objects of a generic type T.
    TypedUF_HWQUPC<T>
    TypedUF_HWQUPC is a generic implementation of a union-find (UF) data structure based on the Height-weighted Quick Union with Path Compression (HWQUPC) algorithm.
